			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<h2><span style="color: #0000ff;">100.Science &amp; Mormonism 2</span></h2>
<p><span style="color: #0000ff;"><em>This is a further discussion of this topic, which will continue in the next podcast. </em></span></p>
