			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<h2>Book of Mormon Discussion</h2>
<p>This discussion includes several topic: deification, Mormons and Moonmen, Joseph Smith&#8217;s great sermon, the King Follett Discourse, but much of the time is about the Book of Mormon. This includes the historicty and the historical questions of the Book and the role of Joseph Smith and God in its foundation.</p>
<p>This program aired 2006-12-17
