		<title>Polygamy: Some Statistics and Some Speculations</title>
		<link>http://mormonmisc.podbean.com/2007/04/25/polygamy-some-statistics-and-some-speculations/</link>
		<comments>http://mormonmisc.podbean.com/2007/04/25/polygamy-some-statistics-and-some-speculations/#comments</comments>
